---
import BuildingImg from '../../../assets/Images/AboutUsPageImg/HistoryImg/Building.png';
import HistoryCall from '../../../assets/Icons/AboutUsIcons/HistoryIcons/historyCall.png';
---

<section class="history-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="history-content">
      <div class="text-content">
        <h2>History of DS Invisible Grills</h2>
        <p>For over 25 years, DS Invisible Grills has been dedicated to redefining home safety with modern solutions that protect without blocking the beauty of your view. What began as a small safety-net installation service has now grown into a trusted brand known for premium invisible grill systems and precision craftsmanship.</p>
        <p>From our early adoption of marine-grade stainless steel wires to today's advanced high-tensile invisible grill technology.</p>
        <button class="enquiry-btn">Enquiry Now <img src={HistoryCall.src} alt="Call Icon" class="btn-icon" /></button>
      </div>
      <div class="image-content">
        <img src={BuildingImg.src} alt="Modern Building" class="building-image" />
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="why-choose-content">
      <div class="image-content">
        <img src={BuildingImg.src} alt="Modern Building" class="building-image" />
      </div>
      <div class="text-content">
        <h2>Why Choose Us?</h2>
        <p>Every home is different — and so is every safety need. That's why our invisible grill systems are engineered with durability, aesthetics, and family protection in mind. With high-grade stainless steel, expert installation, and customizable options, we ensure your balconies and windows stay safe without compromising on design.</p>
        <p>Whether it's safeguarding children, pets, or simply enhancing the look of your home, our solutions blend seamlessly</p>
        <button class="services-btn">Our Services ↗</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .history-section {
    padding: 80px 0;
    background: #F8F8F8;
  }
  
  .container {
    max-width: 1400px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 40px;
  }
  
  .history-content,
  .why-choose-content {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 80px;
    margin-bottom: 120px;
  }
  
  .why-choose-content {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }
  
  .text-content {
    flex: 1;
    max-width: 600px;
  }
  
  .text-content h2 {
    font-size: 48px;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: #333;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }
  
  .text-content p {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: #666;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  
  .enquiry-btn,
  .services-btn {
    background: transparent;
    border: 2px solid #D4A574;
    color: #D4A574;
    padding: 12px 24px;
    border-radius: 25px;
    font-size: 16px;
    cursor: pointer;
    margin-top: 20px;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    width: fit-content;
  }

  .btn-icon {
    width: 24px;
    height: 24px;
    object-fit: contain;
  }
  
  .enquiry-btn:hover,
  .services-btn:hover {
    background: #D4A574;
    color: white;
  }
  
  .image-content {
    flex: 1;
    max-width: 600px;
  }
  
  .building-image {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    object-fit: contain;
    border-radius: 20px;
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .history-content,
    .why-choose-content {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 40px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    
    .text-content h2 {
      font-size: 32px;
    }
    
    .building-image {
      height: auto;
    }
  }
</style>